    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "501135714",
    "title": "無茶は厳禁！",
    "enTitle": "Don't Overdo It! ",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ステイゴールドがトレーニング中に\nケガをしてしまったので保健室に連れてきた。",
            "enText": "As Stay Gold sustained an injury while \ntraining, she was taken to the infirmary.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 1702733145069919122
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -4806424009206198620
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4463166697602624340,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "参ったな。\nだいぶ派手にやらかしちまった。",
            "enText": "You got me there. I managed to \nstuff up spectacularly.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 633061359266455487
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -579940899708878497
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -186803783841277168,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "しばらく安静にしないと\nいけないのはわかっているが……。",
            "enText": "I understand that I should probably \nwind down for a while but…",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 5473557878628302029
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -7850980777347542760
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7642982411227431747,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ここで後れを取ると、\n旅程が大きくズレちまいそうだ。",
            "enText": "If I lag behind now, we'll end up with a \nbig gap in the middle of our journey.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": 34,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 5706687857398659950
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 1276629627987568936
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5179544548997632147
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3784872878591733888,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう、静かに言った彼女。\n有無を言わさぬ気配で、\nトレーニングに戻ろうとしていたが……。",
            "enText": "These were the words spoken quietly by \nthe girl. I could tell she was forcibly \ntrying to return to training but…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "今は休むべき",
                    "enText": "You should rest right now",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "なら、やり方は一任してもらう",
                    "enText": "Then I'll leave it up to you",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": -8465420001480078831
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": -7493993098005180314
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": 5628087301000697010
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5123460821767174695,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "…………",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……引かないぞ。休んでくれ",
                    "enText": "…Let's not make it worse. Just rest for me.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "……引かないよ。休んで",
                    "enText": "…Let's not make it worse. Just rest.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5628968037168203949
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 6106132556633592076
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -5179242210419289294
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4961366725131710160,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "今、無理をしては今後のレースに、\nひいては彼女の人生に大きく響く……。\nそのことを真正面から伝えた。",
            "enText": "If she acts recklessly now, it would affect \nher next races, and end up influencing her \nlife… I confronted her directly with these \nwords.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 6379963712499685459
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": -3895292381433128081
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3329682431498303928,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "なるほど……。\nそれがあんたの矜持か。\n私の、トレーナーとしての。",
            "enText": "I see… So those are you earnest \nwords as my trainer huh.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": 154,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": 887311599889093891
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -9078327683306937151
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4009024847064915299,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "わかったよ。\nその判断を信じるとしよう。",
            "enText": "I got it. I'll trust your judgement.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "voiceIdx": 48,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 7162532309548554751
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 3378305147422695255
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6732210592480355222,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ほう…………。\nそこまで言うからには、\n考えがあるんだよな？",
            "enText": "Oh…… If that's what you're suggesting, \nthen that means you thought this \nthrough?",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 6296826186033742609
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 44,
                    "pathId": -5321830762224076376
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 4042338031494283670
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7724338045549563699,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "今考えうる、ケガに影響の少なそうな\nトレーニング内容を伝えた。\n彼女は納得した様子で実行に移り……。",
            "enText": "I listed out all the gentle exercises I could \nthink of right now. She looked convinced, \nand started to move…",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 2153491781454098177
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -3387265158016735697
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8090829292120597517,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "――いっ……！\nちょっと、これ以上はキツそうだ。",
            "enText": "<i>——Kuh……! </i>Wait a sec, any more \nthan this might be too much.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 109,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 2606747383869505474
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": -95530558000453313
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 2774182957863106241
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4769900320141786560,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "悪いな、どうしても力が入っちまう。\n理屈通りにはいかないもんだな……。",
            "enText": "It's my bad, I got too enthusiastic about \nit. Following my whims may not have \nbeen the best idea hey…",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -7480095341832393478
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -5496053143291630121
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -1159230914518224510
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3475834006276549036,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "体に負担の少ないメニューとはいえ、\nこのケガでは難しいようだ……。\n諦めて、当分は安静にすることとなった。",
            "enText": "Despite coming up with a gentler training \nregime, the injury still seems serious… For \nthe time being, we gave up on training and \nrested.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": -2410673348807189912
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": -3971088576512842131
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5008979843953019040,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "――ふーっ……！",
            "enText": "——<i>Fuu…!</i>",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 59,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -2747804071892714521
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -6024374127464884208
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -164631944038534978,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "いいな！\n水中なら負担は少なそうだ。",
            "enText": "This is good! It seems like there's less \nburden on my body if I exercise in water.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 499782296200208473
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -8575796524392511878
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7100554392962919744,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "それに、ちょっと楽しい。\n普段のトレーニングと違って新鮮だ。",
            "enText": "Also, it's kinda fun, feels sort of fresh \ncompared to normal training.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 735938751793454764
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 7112582571280541867
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 7033408568753948938
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2943142816614173566,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "助かったよ。\nさすがトレーナーだな。\nこの調子でやっていこう！",
            "enText": "I really have to give it to you Trainer, \nyou helped me out. Let's keep it up!",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "voiceIdx": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5875309292555641985
